{"tid":696894,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)侏羅紀世界 神秘電影","createTime":"2018-06-10T13:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T19:59:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea792ea303056f053c5d5942946afd2e65c637b","tid":696894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=98728b55\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0e4dc6cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6376dd51\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e7/Jurassic_Park_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe7%2FJurassic_Park_poster.jpg&h=7dee0461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.侏羅紀公園發生慘劇後22年，最初的公園創辦人約翰&middot;哈蒙德經營的『遺傳科技公司（InGen）』在瀕臨破產下被『馬斯拉尼國際企業（Masrani Corp）』收購。在企業老闆賽門&middot;馬斯拉尼的經營下，昔日公園的所在地「努布拉島」已經被企業重新建造，如今成為了一個安全指數百分之百且嶄新的恐龍主題樂園，並更名為「侏羅紀世界」。久而久之，當公園的遊客們已經開始對恐龍感到厭倦時，企業為了再度提升來遊客人數而決定創造新賣點，在生命開發實驗室的亨利&middot;吳博士在賽門的要求下創造出了一隻基因混合恐龍，命名為「帝王暴龍」.........<br />\n<br />\n2.<img src=\"https://img.cheercut.com/20180606160734_70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.cheercut.com%2F20180606160734_70.jpg&h=96008e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7da3c659\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=PVZoS7DTFeWQ%2FVo7E21pXcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cb9abce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cc082794ca0f797276ebec50ecc8792b48e2fa","tid":696894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c147b9b90f11cd01bc056e5b08e270359cd1915","tid":696894,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e146149217538b14f434b4bfcabe6eb7aa271